<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="keywords" content="">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
</head>
<body style="background:#EFEFEF; overflow:hidden">
<div class="chat-box">
    <div id="setname">
        <input type="text" value="请输入昵称" id="name" onfocus="javascript:this.value=''">
        <a href="javascript:" id="enter" class="btn btn-green">进入聊天室</a>
    </div>
    <div style="display:none" id="chatbox">
        <div class="chatright">
            <h4>欢迎使用简易在线聊天室，本聊天室是基于nodejs + socket.io构建。 <a href="/lab">返回</a></h4>
            <p id="conn-info">正在连接到聊天服务器，请稍后...</p>
            <div class="chatcontent">
                <ul id="chatlist"></ul>
            </div>
            <div class="sendbox">
                <textarea id="senddata" disabled></textarea>
                <button id="send">发送消息<br>Ctrl+Enter</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/js/jquery.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/js/chat.js"></script>
</body>
</html>